sequenceDiagram
  participant User as Operator/API
  participant Svc as Ingestion Service
  participant Conn as Connector
  participant Store as Raw Snapshot Store
  participant DB as PostgreSQL Control Plane
  User->>Svc: extract(org, source, object, optional prior run)
  Svc->>DB: verify registered source/object and resume scope
  Svc->>Conn: extract(object, cursor)
  Conn-->>Svc: records, raw bytes, content type, new cursor
  Svc->>Store: atomic content-addressed write
  Store-->>Svc: manifest, checksum, reuse status
  Svc->>DB: insert/reuse RawSnapshot; complete IngestionRun
  Svc-->>User: run ID, snapshot ID, checksum, row count, cursor
